quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,Darnga konngoowo ɓɗere
  101,2,Hol ko woni Qari*a
  101,3,Hol ko anndin Ma Qari*a
  101,4,ñande yimɓe mba*i no mbeɗon Alla carikon
  101,5,pelle ɗen wa'oya wa hottolle kardaako
  101,6,Tawi ko oon mbo peesirɗe mum teddi
  101,7,Hara himo e nguurndam welɗam
  101,8,Tawi ko oon mbo peesirɗe mum koyi
  101,9,Hoɗorde makko ko jahatnama
  101,10,Ko honɗum anndin maa ko woni ngeen
  101,11,Ko nge yiite wulnge